HEADWORD: Fellow-creature
<hw>Fel"low-crea"ture</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of
the same race or kind; one made by the same Creator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Reason, by which we are raised above our
<qex>fellow-creatures</qex>, the brutes.</q> <rj><qau>I.
Watts.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

